		<div class="comment-body"><p>I&#8217;m happy to say we&#8217;re far, far past using Maven&#8217;s &#8220;examples&#8221;. :-)</p>
<p>In this case, complexity does not flow from what&#8217;s used to describe the build, it comes from the permutations of complex operations that people need in order to configure, build, and deploy their software.</p>
</div>

